    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;PRIZE ANIMALS&quot; is a casual action game in which players collect cute animals with a crane. You can hook the crane's claws into the ring, or go for the antlers and tails. Would you like to collect over 50 different animals in a way that only you can?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Animals around the world</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More than 50 different animals appear.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Animals from disparate habitats will be brought together.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >No worries for beginners</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The number of plays is unlimited, so you can try as many times as you like.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Animals have rings attached to them, so if you have trouble getting them, you can aim for them.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Library mode</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The library records the number of animals you have collected so far.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cute animals can be viewed from various angles.</p>",
